--------------------- Load YOSYS Tool : --------------------- 1. Download oss-cad-suite from https://sites.google.com/view/faulttrackingframework/home
2. Extract the oss-cad-suite
3. Load the start.bat file from the extracted oss-cad folder. ex: ....\oss-cad-suite\start.bat
-------------------------------------------------- OR YOU CAN USE LINUX ENVIRONMENT : -------------------------------------------------- Download YOSYS for Linux: https://yosyshq.net/yosys/download.html
Technology Map Library Available at: https://sites.google.com/view/faulttrackingframework/home
